*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

*       text

*----------------------------------------------------------------------*




MODULE USER_COMMAND_0100 INPUT.

  CASE OK_CODE.

    WHEN 'BACK' OR 'CANC'.

      LEAVE TO SCREEN 0.

    WHEN 'EXIT'.

      LEAVE PROGRAM.

    WHEN 'PDF'.

      PERFORM DOWNLOAD_PDF.

  ENDCASE.

ENDMODULE.




